---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Facials – Bliss Dermacare" description="Professional facial treatments at Bliss Dermacare in Tampa, FL. Dermaplaning, enzyme facials, PRP, chemical peels, diamond glow & more.">

  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="py-14 bg-[#faf9f7] border-b border-neutral-100">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-sm text-neutral-500 mb-4">
        <a href="/services/" class="hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors">All Services</a>
        <span>/</span>
        <span class="text-neutral-900 font-medium">Facials</span>
      </div>
      <span class="text-primary-600 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-xs font-semibold mb-4 block">Skin Treatments</span>
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-4">Facials</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 max-w-xl mx-auto">Professional facials tailored to every skin type and concern. Each treatment is personalized to your skin on the day of your visit.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Featured: Dermaplane Glow Facial -->
  <section class="py-14 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">

      <div class="mb-8 group bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border-2 border-amber-200 hover:border-amber-400 relative">
        <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 z-10"><span class="bg-amber-500 text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">NEW</span></div>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[5fr_7fr]">
          <div class="relative h-56 md:h-auto overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/images/dermaplane-glow-facial.jpg" alt="Dermaplane Glow Facial — professional dermaplaning treatment at Bliss Dermacare" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 to-transparent"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 md:p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-2">Dermaplane Glow Facial</h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm mb-4 max-w-lg">The gold standard of facial exfoliation. A precise surgical scalpel painlessly removes dead skin cells and vellus hair (peach fuzz), revealing a smoother, brighter complexion — and priming your skin to absorb serums up to 70% more effectively. Finishes with a custom brightening serum and hydrating glow mask.</p>
            <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-x-6 gap-y-2 mb-5">
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-neutral-600">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Deep dermaplaning exfoliation</li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Painless peach fuzz &amp; dead cell removal</li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Custom brightening serum infusion</li>
              </ul>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-neutral-600">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Hydrating glow mask included</li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Instantly smoother, more radiant skin</li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Zero downtime</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-6 flex-wrap">
              <div><p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">$105</p><p class="text-xs text-neutral-500">60 minutes</p></div>
              <a href="/book/" data-service-id="dermaplane-glow-facial" class="px-5 py-2.5 bg-amber-500 text-white text-sm font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-amber-600 transition-colors shadow-md">Book Now</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Featured: Smooth Canvas Facial -->
      <div class="mb-8 group bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border-2 border-amber-200 hover:border-amber-400 relative">
        <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 z-10"><span class="bg-amber-500 text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">NEW</span></div>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[5fr_7fr]">
          <div class="relative h-56 md:h-auto overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/images/smooth-canvas-facial.jpg" alt="Smooth Canvas Facial — pore-refining texture treatment at Bliss Dermacare" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 to-transparent"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 md:p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-2">Smooth Canvas Facial</h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm mb-4 max-w-lg">The ultimate skin-prep treatment. A targeted 45-minute ritual that deep-cleanses pores, removes congestion, and refines skin texture so your complexion looks flawless — whether you're prepping for an event, a photoshoot, or simply want consistently smooth, even skin.</p>
            <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-x-6 gap-y-2 mb-5">
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-neutral-600">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Deep-cleanse &amp; pore decongestion</li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>BHA exfoliation for texture refinement</li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Clay mask to absorb excess oil</li>
              </ul>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-neutral-600">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Niacinamide serum for pore tightening</li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Barrier-balancing moisturizer</li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>Ideal for oily, combo &amp; pre-event skin</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-6 flex-wrap">
              <div><p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">$89</p><p class="text-xs text-neutral-500">45 minutes</p></div>
              <a href="/book/" data-service-id="smooth-canvas-facial" class="px-5 py-2.5 bg-amber-500 text-white text-sm font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-amber-600 transition-colors shadow-md">Book Now</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 2-col featured -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-all border-2 border-primary-100 hover:border-primary-300 relative">
          <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 z-10"><span class="bg-primary-600 text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">BESTSELLER</span></div>
          <div class="relative h-52 overflow-hidden"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1570172619644-dfd03ed5d881?w=600&h=400&fit=crop&q=80" alt="Signature Radiance Facial" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" loading="lazy" /><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 to-transparent"></div></div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-2">Signature Radiance Facial</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm mb-4">Deep cleanse, steam, extractions, custom mask &amp; gua sha massage. Visibly brighter skin — every skin type, every time.</p>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between"><div><p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">$99</p><p class="text-xs text-neutral-500">60 minutes</p></div><a href="/book/" data-service-id="signature-radiance-facial" class="px-4 py-2 bg-primary-600 text-white text-sm font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors">Book</a></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-all border-2 border-primary-100 hover:border-primary-300 relative">
          <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 z-10"><span class="bg-amber-500 text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">PREMIUM</span></div>
          <div class="relative h-52 overflow-hidden"><img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/29648626/pexels-photo-29648626.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=600" alt="Vampire Facial PRP" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300" loading="lazy" /><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 to-transparent"></div></div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-2">Vampire Facial (PRP)</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm mb-4">Harness your own growth factors. PRP + microneedling fades scars, reverses aging &amp; resurfaces skin. Visible after 1 session.</p>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between"><div><p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">$380</p><p class="text-xs text-neutral-500">75 min | Series of 3</p></div><a href="/book/" data-service-id="vampire-facial-prp" class="px-4 py-2 bg-primary-600 text-white text-sm font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors">Book</a></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 4-col grid -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-5">
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg transition-all border border-neutral-200"><div class="relative h-32 overflow-hidden"><img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/5069454/pexels-photo-5069454.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=400" alt="Brightening Peel" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300" loading="lazy" /><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/40 to-transparent"></div></div><div class="p-4"><h3 class="text-base font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-1">Brightening Peel</h3><p class="text-neutral-500 text-xs mb-3">Medical-grade chemical exfoliation for texture &amp; hyperpigmentation.</p><div class="flex items-center justify-between"><div><p class="text-lg font-bold text-primary-600">$128</p><p class="text-xs text-neutral-400">45 min</p></div><a href="/book/" data-service-id="brightening-peel" class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-primary-600 text-white text-xs font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors">Book</a></div></div></div>
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg transition-all border border-neutral-200"><div class="relative h-32 overflow-hidden"><img src="/images/diamond-glow.jpg" alt="Diamond Glow" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300" loading="lazy" /><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/40 to-transparent"></div></div><div class="p-4"><h3 class="text-base font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-1">Diamond Glow</h3><p class="text-neutral-500 text-xs mb-3">Diamond-tip resurfacing that buffs away dullness &amp; reveals smoother, glowing skin instantly.</p><div class="flex items-center justify-between"><div><p class="text-lg font-bold text-primary-600">$119</p><p class="text-xs text-neutral-400">50 min</p></div><a href="/book/" data-service-id="diamond-glow" class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-primary-600 text-white text-xs font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors">Book</a></div></div></div>
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg transition-all border border-neutral-200"><div class="relative h-32 overflow-hidden"><img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/3985329/pexels-photo-3985329.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=400" alt="Teen Skincare Facial" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300" loading="lazy" /><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/40 to-transparent"></div></div><div class="p-4"><h3 class="text-base font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-1">Teen Skincare Facial</h3><p class="text-neutral-500 text-xs mb-3">Gentle facial for teens targeting acne &amp; oiliness.</p><div class="flex items-center justify-between"><div><p class="text-lg font-bold text-primary-600">$64</p><p class="text-xs text-neutral-400">45 min</p></div><a href="/book/" data-service-id="teen-skincare-facial" class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-primary-600 text-white text-xs font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors">Book</a></div></div></div>
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg transition-all border border-neutral-200"><div class="relative h-32 overflow-hidden"><img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/3764013/pexels-photo-3764013.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=400" alt="High Frequency Skin Tightening" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300" loading="lazy" /><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/40 to-transparent"></div></div><div class="p-4"><h3 class="text-base font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-1">High Frequency Skin Tightening</h3><p class="text-neutral-500 text-xs mb-3">Electrical current firms, tightens &amp; lifts. Reduces pores, stimulates collagen &amp; clears blemishes.</p><div class="flex items-center justify-between"><div><p class="text-lg font-bold text-primary-600">$95</p><p class="text-xs text-neutral-400">45 min</p></div><a href="/book/" data-service-id="high-frequency-skin-tightening" class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-primary-600 text-white text-xs font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors">Book</a></div></div></div>
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg transition-all border border-neutral-200"><div class="relative h-32 overflow-hidden"><img src="/images/pumpkin-enzyme-facial.jpg" alt="Pumpkin Enzyme Facial" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300" loading="lazy" /><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/40 to-transparent"></div></div><div class="p-4"><h3 class="text-base font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-1">Pumpkin Enzyme Facial</h3><p class="text-neutral-500 text-xs mb-3">Gentle enzyme exfoliation that brightens and smooths — ideal for all skin types, including sensitive.</p><div class="flex items-center justify-between"><div><p class="text-lg font-bold text-primary-600">$85</p><p class="text-xs text-neutral-400">60 min</p></div><a href="/book/" data-service-id="pumpkin-enzyme-facial" class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-primary-600 text-white text-xs font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors">Book</a></div></div></div>
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg transition-all border border-neutral-200"><div class="relative h-32 overflow-hidden"><img src="/images/chlorophyll-skin-tightening-facial.jpg" alt="Chlorophyll Skin Tightening Facial" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300" loading="lazy" /><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/40 to-transparent"></div></div><div class="p-4"><h3 class="text-base font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-1">Chlorophyll Skin Tightening Facial</h3><p class="text-neutral-500 text-xs mb-3">Plant-powered formula visibly reduces fine lines &amp; wrinkles while firming the skin's surface.</p><div class="flex items-center justify-between"><div><p class="text-lg font-bold text-primary-600">$105</p><p class="text-xs text-neutral-400">60 min</p></div><a href="/book/" data-service-id="chlorophyll-skin-tightening-facial" class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-primary-600 text-white text-xs font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors">Book</a></div></div></div>
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg transition-all border border-neutral-200"><div class="relative h-32 overflow-hidden"><img src="/images/pineapple-enzyme-facial.jpg" alt="Pineapple Enzyme Facial" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300" loading="lazy" /><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/40 to-transparent"></div></div><div class="p-4"><h3 class="text-base font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-1">Pineapple Enzyme Facial</h3><p class="text-neutral-500 text-xs mb-3">Bromelain-rich exfoliation that refines pores &amp; evens texture. Perfect for combination skin.</p><div class="flex items-center justify-between"><div><p class="text-lg font-bold text-primary-600">$88</p><p class="text-xs text-neutral-400">60 min</p></div><a href="/book/" data-service-id="pineapple-enzyme-facial" class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-primary-600 text-white text-xs font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors">Book</a></div></div></div>
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg transition-all border border-neutral-200"><div class="relative h-32 overflow-hidden"><img src="/images/skin-recovery-facial.jpg" alt="Skin Recovery Facial" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300" loading="lazy" /><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/40 to-transparent"></div></div><div class="p-4"><h3 class="text-base font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-1">Skin Recovery Facial</h3><p class="text-neutral-500 text-xs mb-3">Multi-vitamin infusion deeply nourishes &amp; replenishes dry and dehydrated skin back to radiance.</p><div class="flex items-center justify-between"><div><p class="text-lg font-bold text-primary-600">$92</p><p class="text-xs text-neutral-400">60 min</p></div><a href="/book/" data-service-id="skin-recovery-facial" class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-primary-600 text-white text-xs font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors">Book</a></div></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Also Explore -->
  <section class="py-10 bg-neutral-50 border-t border-neutral-100">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-neutral-400 mb-4">Also Explore</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a href="/services/lash-brow-body/" class="px-4 py-2 bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-full text-sm text-neutral-700 hover:border-primary-300 hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors">Lash, Brow &amp; Body</a>
        <a href="/services/advanced-treatments/" class="px-4 py-2 bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-full text-sm text-neutral-700 hover:border-primary-300 hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors">Advanced Treatments</a>
        <a href="/services/semipermanent-makeup/" class="px-4 py-2 bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-full text-sm text-neutral-700 hover:border-primary-300 hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors">Semipermanent Makeup</a>
        <a href="/services/ancillary/" class="px-4 py-2 bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-full text-sm text-neutral-700 hover:border-primary-300 hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors">Ancillary Services</a>
        <a href="/services/packages/" class="px-4 py-2 bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-full text-sm text-neutral-700 hover:border-primary-300 hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors">Seasonal Packages</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Book CTA -->
  <section class="py-14 bg-neutral-900 text-white text-center">
    <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif mb-4">Ready to book a facial?</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-400 mb-8">Choose your facial and request a time that works for you. We'll confirm within 24 hours.</p>
      <a href="/book/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-primary-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-primary-700 transition-all font-medium shadow-lg">
        Request Booking
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
